fields.error_warning_message: IRF Number must start with station code
Number of PVs must be entered
Number of Suspects should be entered
Location should be entered
Staff name who filled out the form must be entered
Either Contact or Staff must be chosen for how interception was made
How sure are you that you were right to intercept should be entered
Interceptee name must be entered
Interceptee gender must be entered
"Why did potential victim stop?" should be entered
Must be current or prior date
Birthdate must be current or prior date
Should have attachment with option "Original Form"
Job should be entered if any of 4.12 through 4.16 are selected
Promised pay should be entered if any of 4.12 through 4.16 are selected
Normal pay should be entered if any of 4.12 through 4.16 are selected
Profile information should be provided
Area/Industry information should be provided
Resources/safety information should be provided
At least one interceptee must be entered
PV count does not match the number of interceptees identified as PV
Suspect count does not match the number of interceptees identified as suspects
MPA and Agent data should not be entered when N/A checkbox is selected
Agent information should not be present when the N/A checkbox is selected
Area information should be provided
Industry information should be provided
Follow-up call facts must be entered when follow-up call has been completed
Date IRF received must be populated
Narrative must be entered
